OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome late
OL,6,Fsunny spells and a few showers this
OL,7,Fevening. Then dry overnight with long
OL,8,Fclear spells developing. Touch of
OL,9,Ffrost possible in sheltered spots.
OL,10,FWinds easing.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FA dry and largely sunny start,
OL,13,Fsome cloud will develop for the
OL,14,Fafternoon but it will remain dry.
OL,15,FNorthwesterly breeze continuing to
OL,16,Fease.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
