OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FDry
OL,6,Fmorning with sunny spells Saturday,
OL,7,Fbut cloud increasing with some rain
OL,8,Flater. Rain clearing overnight then
OL,9,Fsunny spells and a few showers. Rather
OL,10,Fcloudy Monday with occasional rain.
